official_title: A bill to terminate the authorization of the Tocks Island Reservoir project, Pennsylvania, New Jersey, and New York.

summary.text: Terminates the authorization of the Tocks Island Reservoir project, Pennsylvania, New Jersey, and New York and transfers all property acquired pursuant to the authorization for such project to the Secretary of the Interior for management by the National Park Service.
